            {
                "name": "Novelists",
                "url": "/topics/novelists"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/amy_waldman_495811",
        "quote": "As a novelist, you deepen your characters as you go, adding layers. As a reporter, you try to peel layers away: observing subjects enough to get beneath the surface, re-questioning a source to find the facts. But these processes aren't so different.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Amy Waldman",
            "url": "/quotes/amy_waldman_495811"
        },
        "topics": [
